sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client (admin)
    participant P as Permissions
    participant Ctl as OrdersController
    participant DS as OrderDetailsService
    participant US as OrderUpdateService
    participant DB as Prisma / Postgres
    C->>P: GET /orders/:id (orders.view)
    P->>Ctl: authorized
    Ctl->>DS: getOrderDetails(id)
    DS->>DB: order.findFirst({ id, deleted_at:null }) — all types, not scoped
    alt not found
        DS-->>C: 404
    else found
        DS->>DB: onsite join + resolve creator/plan/refund ledger
        DS-->>Ctl: OrderDetailsResponseDto
        Ctl-->>C: 200
    end
    Note over C,US: PATCH /:id or /:id/sales-rep → US validates + writes (status gate),<br/>audits, then returns the refreshed aggregate
